{
  "page": "Hornoth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Hornoth</b> is a ruined city in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki_sea\" title=\"Dothraki sea\">Dothraki sea</a>, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Sarnor\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Kingdom of Sarnor</a>. It was located near where the <a href=\"/index.php/Sarne\" title=\"Sarne\">Sarne</a> turned north. Hornoth and <a href=\"/index.php/Kyth\" title=\"Kyth\">Kyth</a> were destroyed by rival <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">khals</a></i> after the fall of <a href=\"/index.php/Sallosh\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sallosh\">Sallosh</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hornoth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_beyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNew